    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> This would work, but [attr=value] selectors are known to be slow. Not sure if its measurable on such a small list, though.\n\nYes, first we use it, and if it's slow we see what to do. I could not find any good recent reference stating attribute selector inside a css file is slow.\n",
